>> source: https://www.allrecipes.com/recipe/237469/chia-coconut-pudding-with-coconut-milk/
>> serves: 6
>> total time: 30 minutes

Whisk together sweetened and @sweetened coconut milk{2%cups}, @unsweetened coconut milk{6%Tbsp}, @agave nectar{1%Tbsp}, @vanilla extract{1/2%tsp}, @cinnamon{1/4%tsp}, and @salt{1%pinch} in a #bowl{}; stir in @chia seeds{1/2%cup}. Allow mixture to soak until thickened, at least ~{20%minutes}, or cover the bowl with plastic wrap and refrigerate overnight.

Stir pudding and top with @strawberries (optional){1/2%cup}, @toasted coconut (optional){}, and @boba pearls (optional){}.
